{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset includes 26 million ratings and 750,000 tag applications for all 45,000 movies provided by 270,000 users.",
    "A subset of 3000 samples with movie titles and release years associated with the movie cast was sampled from the Movies dataset.",
    "The task is to predict the cast of a movie based on the movie's name and release year.",
    "The few-shot prompt contains a few examples mapping a movie's name and release year to its cast.",
    "The prompt is in the following format: \"Query: What actors played in the x movie y?\""
  ]
}